Hello! This file is just a placeholder, since this is the "unstable" branch
of Valkey, the place where all the development happens.

Release notes for this branch reflect only publicly merged PRs that carry the
release-notes label; the notes live in the "## Unreleased" block below. This
file gets forked into another branch every time there is a partial feature
freeze in order to eventually create a new stable release.

Usually "unstable" is stable enough for you to use it in development environments
however you should never use it in production environments. It is possible
to download the latest stable release here:

    https://valkey.io/download/

More information is available at https://valkey.io

Happy hacking!

